data.description: Popular Pine Spring plan across from GREENBELT.  Spacious family room with open area to kitchen.  Family room has barn door type shutters and tray ceiling.  Study-den with double doors for privacy. Huge kitchen with granite counters, upgraded cabinets, stylish tile splash, SS range & oven, DW and MW.   Master suite has tray ceiling and is enhanced with triple windows.  Master bath has dual sinks, large tile shower, medicine cabinet & walk-in closet.  Guest bedroom & bathroom split. Patio faces east and overlooks  a delightful backyard. Extended garage.  New roof October 2017.
